Rayon Jefter WILLIAMS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0824 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. April 12, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for belated appeal filed in case number 2D19-0824 is duplicative of the relief sought in case number 2D18-3282. Therefore, case number 2D19-0824 is dismissed.

NORTHCUTT, SALARIO, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ.T Concur.
